#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn7.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Arahantavagga "
msgstr "1. The Perfected Ones "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Suddhikasutta "
msgstr "7. With Bhāradvāja the Pure "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.166, pts2ed1.355, sc1
msgctxt "sn7.7:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.7:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho suddhikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then the brahmin Bhāradvāja the Pure went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with him. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.7:1.3"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side, "

msgctxt "sn7.7:1.4"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho suddhikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "and recited this verse in his presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
#. VAR: Na brāhmaṇo → nābrāhmaṇo (?)
msgctxt "sn7.7:2.1"
msgid "“Na brāhmaṇo sujjhati koci, "
msgstr "“No brahmin in the world is ever purified "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:2.2"
msgid "Loke sīlavāpi tapokaraṃ; "
msgstr "even though he’s ethical and mortifies himself. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:2.3"
msgid "Vijjācaraṇasampanno, "
msgstr "But one accomplished in knowledge and conduct "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:2.4"
msgid "So sujjhati na aññā itarā pajā”ti. "
msgstr "is purified, not these commoners.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn7.7:3.1"
msgid "“Bahumpi palapaṃ jappaṃ, "
msgstr "“Even one who mutters many invocations "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:3.2"
msgid "na jaccā hoti brāhmaṇo; "
msgstr "is no brahmin by birth "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:3.3"
msgid "Antokasambu saṅkiliṭṭho, "
msgstr "if they’re filthy and corrupt within, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:3.4"
msgid "kuhanaṃ upanissito. "
msgstr "supporting themselves by fraud. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn7.7:4.1"
msgid "Khattiyo brāhmaṇo vesso, "
msgstr "Regardless of whether you’re an aristocrat, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:4.2"
msgid "Suddo caṇḍālapukkuso; "
msgstr "a brahmin, merchant, worker, or an outcaste or scavenger—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:4.3"
msgid "Āraddhavīriyo pahitatto, "
msgstr "if you’re energetic and resolute, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:4.4"
msgid "Niccaṃ daḷhaparakkamo; "
msgstr "always staunchly vigorous, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:4.5"
msgid "Pappoti paramaṃ suddhiṃ, "
msgstr "you’ll attain the highest happiness. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.7:4.6"
msgid "Evaṃ jānāhi brāhmaṇā”ti. "
msgstr "Know that for a fact, brahmin.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.356, sc5
msgctxt "sn7.7:5.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, suddhikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he had spoken, the brahmin Bhāradvāja the Pure said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn7.7:5.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama …” … "

msgctxt "sn7.7:5.3"
msgid "aññataro ca panāyasmā bhāradvājo arahataṃ ahosīti. "
msgstr "And Venerable Bhāradvāja became one of the perfected."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
